<font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3"><b>Mission</b></font><br>
<blockquote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">
<ul>
<li>Sharing the gospel of salvation through preaching the Word of God in meetings, Church gatherings, over the Internet and broadcast media.</li>
<li>Strengthening Churches around the world by sharing the Word of God to believers to bring them to a closer walk with the Lord God as the Lord opens the doors.</li><li>To pray for the lost souls and souls in need by effective ministering through the ministry of prayer, in organized fasting prayer meetings and through intercessory prayers.</li>
<li>To demonstrate the love of God to the people in need by furthering social well being of the downtrodden and under privileged, sponsoring or coordinating social wellness oriented benevolence projects providing leadership and assistance through the grace and mercy of God as God enables us. </li>
</ul>
</font></blockquote>
